   "source": [
# 💰 SpendSense: Personal Expense Analysis & Budget Insights

A data science project to analyse personal spending patterns using 
EDA, time-series forecasting (Prophet), and machine learning 
(KMeans, Linear Regression).

**Author:** Rajat Tyagi | [GitHub](https://github.com/tyagirajat154)
    "\n",
    "SpendSense is a personal expense analysis project that uses data science techniques to understand spending patterns, forecast future expenses, and group transactions by behaviour. The dataset contains daily transaction records including date, category, amount, payment mode, and description.\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
