    "## 14. Prophet – 30-Day Expense Forecasting\n",
    "\n",
    "Prophet is a time-series forecasting model developed by Facebook. It captures trends and seasonal patterns in the data to predict future spending. Here we forecast the next 30 days of expenses."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 17,
   "id": "69566fee",
